                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d220">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Pekin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-11-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 19, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Conger reports that by a new Imperial decree, dated November 13, punishment
                    of persons mentioned in Imperial decree of September 25 is fixed. In every case
                    the punishment is totally inadequate and is considered as farcical by the
                    diplomatic corps.)</p>
            </div>
